div.p: Hi everyone! If you somehow landed on this page, please really consider supporting my work monetarily if you are able to and you like what I do. I am currently going through a very difficult time in my life and need all the help I can get. No amount is too small, any support whatsoever will be greatly appreciated and will have a huge impact for me at this time in my life. Thank you!
All the ways in which you can support me can be found on this page (I am the owner of that site).
I'm a 29 years old software developer, designer and amateur music producer and artist from the Czech Republic.

Nowadays I don't have that much time for music and art anymore, so currently I'm focusing mainly on programming. For my open-source contributions, check my GitHub profile or my portfolio to see my projects.

Most of my artistic work is made for NeonMob, where I've been publishing professionally since early 2016, releasing 6 series since then. You can view my profile for my work there (apparently NeonMob has shut down and I can't find my profile archived anywhere, so for now the closest alternative is my Behance account - view here).
For my original music, check my SoundCloud . Also check my YouTube for more music and videos.
If you like what I do or what I'm about and want to support me monetarily, any amount, one-time or monthly, will be much appreciated. Thank you!
